{"title":"借助 Safari 调试苹果手机上的 webView","date":"2018-07-25T07:21:07.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jul 25, 2018","L":"07/25/2018","MM-DD":"07-25"},"link":"2018/debug-webview-with-safari","tags":["webView"],"categories":["iOS"],"updated":"2020-01-26T05:50:47.786Z","content":"<h2 id=\"iPhone-真机-模拟器设置\">iPhone 真机/模拟器设置<a href=\"2018/debug-webview-with-safari#iPhone-真机-模拟器设置\"></a></h2><p>需要如下图所示，点击“设置” → 点击 “Safari 浏览器” → 点击“高级” → 打开“Web 检查器”。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<img src=\"/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/open-the-web-inspector.jpg\" class=\"article-img\" title=\"打开 Web 检查器\">\n\n<p>若模拟器中无“Web 检查器”选项，无需设置。</p>\n<h2 id=\"Safari-设置\">Safari 设置<a href=\"2018/debug-webview-with-safari#Safari-设置\"></a></h2><p>打开 Mac 电脑中的 Safari 浏览器，打开偏好设置，点击菜单中的“高级”选项卡，勾选“在菜单栏中显示“开发”菜单”</p>\n<img src=\"/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/safari-perferences-advanced.jpg\" class=\"article-img\" title=\"Safari-偏好设置-高级\">\n\n<h2 id=\"进入检查器\">进入检查器<a href=\"2018/debug-webview-with-safari#进入检查器\"></a></h2><p>在手机/模拟器中打开浏览器/App中的某个网页，在 Mac 中打开 Safari，在“开发”中找到目标设备。</p>\n<img src=\"/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/select-target-device.jpg\" class=\"article-img\" title=\"选择目标设备\">\n\n<blockquote>\n<p>如果你选择的是模拟器，但是开发列表中未出现，重启 Safari 即可。因为必须确保先打开模拟器，再打开 Safari。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>点击目标设备中需要查看的网址，便会弹出这个页面对应的检查器。</p>\n<img src=\"/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/web-inspector.jpg\" class=\"article-img\" title=\"网页检查器\">","prev":{"title":"Git 手册之 Mac 上给 Git 设置 SOCKS5/HTTP 代理","link":"2018/set-up-sock5-or-http-proxy-for-git-on-mac"},"next":{"title":"App Store 审核经验","link":"2018/review-experience"},"plink":"https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/","toc":[{"title":"iPhone 真机/模拟器设置","id":"iPhone-真机-模拟器设置","index":"1"},{"title":"Safari 设置","id":"Safari-设置","index":"2"},{"title":"进入检查器","id":"进入检查器","index":"3"}],"copyright":{"author":"FiTeen","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/\" title=\"借助 Safari 调试苹果手机上的 webView\">https://blog.fiteen.top/2018/debug-webview-with-safari/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}